'''[[台灣|台灣]]'''被認爲是亚洲[[女同性恋|女同性恋]]、[[男同性恋|男同性恋]]、[[双性恋|双性恋]]（LGB）權益方面最进步的地區，<ref name="quartz-ssm">{{cite news|last1=Steger|first1=Isabella|title=In a first for Asia, Taiwan legalized same-sex marriage—with caveats|url=https://qz.com/1621783/taiwan-becomes-first-country-in-asia-to-legalize-same-sex-marriage/|accessdate=2019-05-20|work=Quartz|language=en|quote=Though Taiwan is widely regarded as the most progressive place in Asia for gay rights—the closest country in the region that has legalized gay marriage is Australia—conservative groups have long tried to pressure legislators to pass a law that does not grant same-sex unions equal rights to heterosexual ones.|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606212917/https://qz.com/1621783/taiwan-becomes-first-country-in-asia-to-legalize-same-sex-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是在[[跨性別|跨性別]]權益方面，相對於[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]和[[以色列|以色列]]較為保守。<ref>{{Cite web|title=紀惠容專欄：看見跨性別，性別選擇是人權（紀惠容）|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20191027/FBRPWM63J4X4JI5KVXUU4FKIQ4/|accessdate=|author=|date=|last=|first=|format=|publisher=|language=zh-tw|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20201101172026/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20191027/FBRPWM63J4X4JI5KVXUU4FKIQ4/|archive-date=2020-11-01|access-date=2020-11-01|website=蘋果新聞網}}</ref>根据同性恋維權人士的说法，台灣很少發生反[[同性戀|同性戀]]的暴力行為，[[警方|警方]]對同志友善空間施壓的情況逐漸減少<ref>{{cite web|title=2009 Human Rights Reports: Taiwan|url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/2009/eap/135990.htm|accessdate=2015-12-21|dead-url=no|quote=There are no laws prohibiting homosexual activities. According to homosexual rights activists, antihomosexual violence was rare, but societal discrimination against lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender (LGBT) persons with HIV and AIDS was a problem. LGBT rights activists said instances of police pressure to close gay- and lesbian-friendly bars and bookstores decreased.|website=美國政府|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222105718/http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/2009/eap/135990.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Country Reports on Human Rights Practices for 2014: Taiwan|url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/humanrightsreport/index.htm?year=2014&dlid=236478#wrapper|accessdate=2015-12-21|dead-url=no|quote=instances of police pressure on LGBT-friendly bars and bookstores were rare and continued to decrease.|website=美國政府|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222090939/http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/humanrightsreport/index.htm?year=2014&dlid=236478#wrapper}}</ref>。男女[[同性性行为|同性性行为]]均合法，并且在2017年5月[[司法院大法官|司法院大法官]]做出釋字第748號解釋<ref>{{Cite web|title=釋字第748號解釋|url=http://cons.judicial.gov.tw/jcc/zh-tw/jep03/show?expno=748|access-date=2021-08-10|last=司法院|work=cons.judicial.gov.tw|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2019-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420160723/http://cons.judicial.gov.tw/jcc/zh-tw/jep03/show?expno=748|dead-url=no}}</ref>，宣告「未使同性二人建立永久結合關係」屬[[違憲|違憲]]，應於解釋後二年修法，[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]于2019年5月24日合法化。但是，同性伴侣目前无法共同收养子女，僅容許繼親收養。

行政院于2003年首次提出对同性婚姻的法律承认。但是，该法案当时遭到了强烈反对，尚未获得表决。在反歧視法方面，分別在2003年和2007年制定了《[[性別平等教育法|性別平等教育法]]》和《[[性別工作平等法|性別工作平等法]]》，保障教育和工作領域不得有性別、性傾向之差別待遇。在2011年《[[性別平等教育法|性別平等教育法]]》修正條文中實施[[性別平等教育|性別平等教育]]，以教育方式教導尊重[[多元性別|多元性別]]（指性別除[[生理性別|生理性別]]外，還包括[[性傾向|性傾向]]、[[性別特質|性別特質]]、[[性別認同|性別認同]]）差異，消除[[性別歧視|性別歧視]]，促進性別地位實質平等。

中華民國[[司法院大法官|司法院大法官]]於2017年5月24日釋憲，《[[中華民國民法|中華民國民法]]》第4編親屬第2章婚姻規定違憲，要求兩年內修正或制定相關保障同性婚姻法律。根据法院的裁决，如果立法機關在2019年5月24日前未完成修法，「同性婚姻」將自动合法。<ref name=":1">{{cite act|title=Judicial Yuan Interpretation No. 185|type=Constitutional Interpretation|language=en|date=1984-01-27|url=http://www.judicial.gov.tw/constitutionalcourt/EN/p03_01.asp?expno=185|access-date=2018-04-09|archive-date=2017-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025015253/http://www.judicial.gov.tw/constitutionalcourt/EN/p03_01.asp?expno=185|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Wu|first=J.R.|date=2017-05-24|title=Taiwan court rules in favor of same-sex marriage, first in Asia|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-taiwan-lgbt-marriage/taiwan-court-rules-in-favor-of-same-sex-marriage-first-in-asia-idUSKBN18K0UN|work=Reuters|location=Taipei|access-date=2018-04-08|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608140240/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-taiwan-lgbt-marriage/taiwan-court-rules-in-favor-of-same-sex-marriage-first-in-asia-idUSKBN18K0UN|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年5月17日，《[[司法院釋字第七四八號解釋施行法|司法院釋字第七四八號解釋施行法]]》三讀通過，5月22日經總統[[蔡英文|蔡英文]]公布，於5月24日生效，使中華民國成為亞洲第一個全國性承認同性婚姻的國家。<ref>{{cite news|title=Taiwan legalises same-sex marriage, a first in Asia|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-05-17/taiwan-legalises-same-sex-marriage/11124868|accessdate=2019-05-20|work=ABC News|publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|date=2019-05-17|language=en-AU|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528054655/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-05-17/taiwan-legalises-same-sex-marriage/11124868|dead-url=no}}</ref>
