2008年11月，經[[台灣TG蝶園|台灣TG蝶園]]的倡議，内政部在一项行政命令中规定，跨性別和雙性人必須「摘除腺體」，以改变其个人文件上的合法性别，不再「須建立另一性別的陰部構造」。<ref name="transgender">{{cite news|last=Yiu|first=Derek|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-allow-gender-change-without-surgery-month251214/|title=Taiwan to allow gender change without surgery in a month|date=25 December 2014|work=Gay Star News|access-date=24 May 2017|archive-date=25 March 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190325101816/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-allow-gender-change-without-surgery-month251214/|url-status=live}}</ref>2014年底讨论了取消手术要求的计划，但没有实施。<ref name="transgender"/><ref>{{cite news|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|url=https://www.new7.com.tw/NewsView.aspx?t=&i=TXT20170607172235X5P|script-title=zh:【同婚進行曲】「性別變更免摘除性器官」懸而未決|trans-title=[The March for Same-sex Marriage] "Gender change without surgery' left undecided|date=15 June 2017|language=zh|work=The Journalist Taiwan|access-date=13 April 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413185552/https://www.new7.com.tw/NewsView.aspx?t=&i=TXT20170607172235X5P|archive-date=13 April 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>2019年10月，一名跨性别女性试图更改其国民身份证上的指定性别。她当地的户籍办公室拒绝了她的要求，因为她只提供了性别不安的诊断证据，并没有提供变性手术的证据。向她的当地政府訴願没有成功。台北市高级行政法院于2021年9月对此案作出裁决，允许她在没有变性手术证据的情况下将其性别列为女性。台北高等行政法院根据宪法作出决定強迫手術嚴重侵害當事人身體健康完整、人格權與人性尊嚴。此外，法院引用了以前的法律解释，得出结论認為基本权利的限制必须通过法律进行或以法律为根据。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Liu |first1=Shih-yi |last2=Teng |first2=Pei-ju |title=Taiwan court rules to allow trans woman's ID card gender change request |url=https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202109240019 |access-date=1 October 2021 |agency=Central News Agency |date=24 September 2021 |archive-date=2021-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001065741/https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202109240019 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/life/taiwan-court-rules-against-proof-of-surgery-requirement-in-massive-win-for-transgender-rights/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-12-19 |archive-date=2021-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210927214229/https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/life/taiwan-court-rules-against-proof-of-surgery-requirement-in-massive-win-for-transgender-rights/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>  

2013年8月，台灣政府決定不撤銷一對跨性別吳伊婷與吳芷儀的婚姻關係，這是台灣首次同性婚姻成功的案例。<ref>{{cite news|last=Yiu|first=Derek|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-same-sex-transgender-marriage-can-stay070813|title=Taiwan: same-sex transgender marriage can stay|date=7 August 2013|work=Gay Star News|access-date=24 May 2017|archive-date=25 March 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190325181707/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-same-sex-transgender-marriage-can-stay070813/|url-status=live}}</ref>

