=== 宗教 ===
[[兔兒神|兔兒神]]是中国道教（中國民間宗教）与同性恋关系的媒人，是同性恋爱情的神灵。2006年，卢伟明在新北市永和区为兔兒神创建了一座寺庙。<ref>{{cite web|title=Praying for a soul mate at Rabbit Temple|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/lifestyle/people/2015/01/26/praying-for-a-soul-mate-at-rabbit-temple/|accessdate=2020-07-23|date=2015-01-26|last=Gold|first=Michael|work=The Star Online|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518192317/https://www.thestar.com.my/lifestyle/people/2015/01/26/praying-for-a-soul-mate-at-rabbit-temple/}}</ref>每年大约有9000名同性恋朝圣者前往圣殿祈祷，特别是为一个伴侣祈祷。该庙还为同性伴侣举行结婚仪式。它是世界上唯一针对同性恋者的宗教圣地。<ref>{{cite web|title=Taiwan's gays pray for soul mates at 'Rabbit' temple|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/taiwan-gay-temple/taiwans-gays-pray-for-soul-mates-at-rabbit-temple-idINKBN0KS0R120150119|accessdate=2020-07-23|date=2015-01-19|last=Gold|first=Michael|work=Reuters|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518025222/https://www.reuters.com/article/taiwan-gay-temple/taiwans-gays-pray-for-soul-mates-at-rabbit-temple-idINKBN0KS0R120150119}}</ref>

